political and economic perspectives.
</P>
<P>
Jovanovic said Yugoslavia is interested in participating in a
number of economic projects on the island, including some in the
tourism sector.
</P>
<P>
The Yugoslav foreign minister is scheduled to meet with Cuban
Foreign Investment and Economic Cooperation Minister Martha Lomas,
during which an investment promotion and protection accord will be
signed.
</P>
