<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, August 28 (Xinhua) -- Tunis Stock Exchange index closed
at 1,389.26 points on Monday, down 0.11 percent from Friday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
According to the daily bulletin of the bourse, 43,045 shares
changed hands in 266 deals, and the turnover was 1,008,498 dinars
(about 730,795 U.S. dollars). 
</P>
