<HEADLINE> Website for National Students Games Launched </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
CHENGDU, August 28 (Xinhua) -- A website for the Sixth
National Students Games was launched today in Chengdu, capital of
southwest China's Sichuan Province.
</P>
<P>
Visitors can learn almost anything about the event through the
website: www.2000nsgames.net, which was launched by the Sichuan
provincial education department.
</P>
<P>
An information center for the games also began operation today.
More than 300 Chinese and foreign journalists will cover the games
which will open on September 3 in Chengdu. 
</P>
</TEXT>
