the pressure of profit-taking in the banking and property sectors.
</P>
<P>
Sub-indices of Finance, Properties and Industry &AMP; Commerce
declined by 3.33 percent, 1.35 percent and 0.11 percent
respectively while that of Utilities picked up 0.09 percent.
