see attitude of most investors ahead of Wednesday's expiration of
the Hang Seng August futures, which could affect the market's
short-term direction.
</P>
<P>
China-related shares ended mixed with the Hang Seng China
Enterprises Index rising 0.91 percent and the Hang Seng China-
Affiliated Corp Index dropping 0.85 percent.
</P>
