<HEADLINE> Guangzhou TV Programs Shown in Macao </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, August 28 (Xinhua) -- Beginning Monday night, the
Chinese TV channel of the Macao Broadcast and Television Company
is scheduled to provide programs produced by the Guangzhou TV
Station.
</P>
<P>
Covering news documentary, entertainment and TV play, the TV
programs will show the big economic and social changes that have
taken place in the neighboring Guangzhou and other cities of
Guangdong Province, pioneers in China's reform and opening-up.
</P>
<P>
The programs will be broadcast 30 times each Monday, Wednesday
and Friday nights.
</P>
<P>
A similar TV festival to exhibit programs from the Guangzhou TV
Station had been held in Macao last year. 
</P>
