WASHINGTON, August 27 (Xinhua) -- Top seed Magnus Norman scored
a three-set victory over fellow Swede Thomas Enqvist to return his
title at the 415,200 U.S. dollars Hamlet Cup tennis event in
Commack of New York on Sunday.
</P>
